00037 /// a single controlled vocabulary term
00038 struct Term
00039 {
00040     typedef unsigned int id_type;
00041     typedef std::vector<id_type> id_list; 
00042 
00043     std::string prefix;
00044     id_type id;
00045     std::string name;
00046     std::string def;
00047     id_list parentsIsA;
00048     id_list parentsPartOf;
00049     std::vector<std::string> exactSynonyms;
00050     bool isObsolete;
00051 
00052     Term()
00053     :   id(std::numeric_limits<int>::max()), isObsolete(false)
00054     {}
00055 };

00058 ///
00059 /// Represents a selectively parsed OBO file.
00060 ///
00061 /// Note that the following are currently ignored during parsing:
00062 /// - comments
00063 /// - dbxrefs
00064 /// - synonym tags other than exact_synonym
00065 /// - non-Term stanzas
00066 /// - obsolete Terms
00067 ///
00068 struct OBO
